{"tid":296557,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"多唔多人覺得自己有抑鬱/暴躁 既症狀","createTime":"2017-06-24T16:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T17:20:43.000Z","uid":62225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ac98e04ba0ac7387bb5b798bdeba90c5960fcd","tid":296557,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:22:20.000Z","msg":"遇到好多人對身邊既人無乜安全感，生活都無黎精彩，覺得自己好廢好無用。<br />\n情緒就好自然會有d抑鬱/暴躁，聽落都會幾擔心！"},{"pid":"738e69ab041850f5b146791ec68d2fc1e3bdb27c","tid":296557,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"香港地冇先唔正常"},{"pid":"8495dc47ea4222302d48e66fbc0c2049191e1e09","tid":296557,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cacaa2c7710ebcafe4fd487d67b85a93ffd568d6","tid":296557,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:23:48.000Z","msg":"<ins>上網政府話抑鬱係這樣</ins><br />\n<br />\n抑鬱症在過去曾被泛指為「神經衰弱」，屬於輕度的精神科病症。病人情緒會出現障礙，引致生理及心理失衡，情緒會持續低落，對事物失去興趣或動力，思想變得負面，因而影響到正常的社交生活。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國精神醫學會的診斷標準，抑鬱症的定義是：病人於持續兩星期以上，有五個或以上已既定的生理或心理症狀，當中必須包括情緒低落及/或失去動力，而且此病持續為病人帶來明顯的情緒困擾及/或嚴重損害其日常生活功能。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www21.ha.org.hk/smartpatient/tc/chronicdiseases_zone/details.html?id=175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww21.ha.org.hk%2Fsmartpatient%2Ftc%2Fchronicdiseases_zone%2Fdetails.html%3Fid%3D175&d=yQPbVcWOTxYQmEQ14OvDCYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=04222a70\" target=\"_blank\">http://www21.ha.org.hk/smartpatient/tc/chronicdiseases_zone/details.html?id=175</a>"},{"pid":"e1ada20d886c651291d4857ecc80943bd64792a8","tid":296557,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港地冇先唔正常</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好x慘，真"},{"pid":"81ed08e32b26f469eff0a9fbe41d642c809fc0bf","tid":296557,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src